    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>,<strong> chipotle paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> then bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
